"```sql\nSELECT AVG(TIME_TO_SEC(SUBSTRING_INDEX(results.time, ':', -1)) + \n           60 * TIME_TO_SEC(SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(results.time, ':', 1), ':', -1)) + \n           3600 * CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(results.time, ':', 1) AS UNSIGNED)) AS average_time_seconds, \n       races.year \nFROM results \nJOIN races ON results.raceId = races.raceId \nWHERE results.time IS NOT NULL \n  AND races.year < 1975 \n  AND results.position = 1 \nGROUP BY races.year;\n```"